      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly a showroom-quality find for a discerning buyer. The exterior paint is flawless, maintaining its original deep luster without a single swirl or scratch, and the interior still carries a fresh, like-new feel with no signs of wear. Mechanically, the car is perfect, having been meticulously maintained with all service records up to date. You can expect a smooth, powerful driving experience that feels exactly as it did the day it rolled off the lot.",
