    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable daily driver that gets the job done? This vehicle is in honest, fair condition and is ready to take you wherever you need to go! While it shows some character from previous adventures, it remains a solid and functional choice for anyone seeking dependable transportation at a great value. It\u2019s a practical ride with plenty of life left for its next owner!",
