    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for a buyer looking for a major restoration project or a source for parts. The exterior shows significant signs of age, including heavy rust along the lower body panels, bubbling paint, and several noticeable dents. Mechanically, the engine requires a complete overhaul as it currently struggles to idle and has multiple fluid leaks, while the transmission exhibits slipping between gears. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with several tears in the seats and a cracked dashboard. Please be aware that this car will likely need to be towed from the lot and will require substantial investment to be roadworthy again.",
