      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to be parting with this beauty, but it\u2019s time for it to find a new home. This car is in absolute mint condition\u2014it seriously looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, always kept it tucked away in the garage, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and meticulously cared for, you\u2019ve found it. I'd love for you to come by and see it for yourself\u2014I promise you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 46500.0,
